e website operated by Drievu Limited (",["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-xs","children":"drievu.com"}],"), including our digital scoping wizards, system configurators, and initial consultative engineering reviews."]}],["$","p",null,{"children":"By accessing this website or submitting an engineering scoping review request, you agree to be bound by these Terms. If you are entering into these Terms on behalf of a commercial entity, housing association, or public-sector body, you represent that you possess the legal authority to bind that organization."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display font-medium text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-slate tracking-tight border-b border-brand-grey/20 pb-3","children":"2. Interactive System Builder & Indicative Estimates"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Our front-of-house Interactive System Builder provides deterministic, rule-based engineering calculations regarding video storage capacities (in Terabytes), hardware channel counts, and network switch sizing based on our deployed product range."}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-brand-slate/80","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"font-medium text-brand-slate","children":"Indicative Nature:"}]," All outputs generated by the System Builder are strictly indicative engineering estimates intended to assist specifiers and property managers during initial project discovery. They do not constitute a binding financial quote, contract of sale, or formal design proposal."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"font-medium text-brand-slate","children":"No Automated AI Scoring:"}]," Drievu evaluates system integrity through verifiable electrical and mechanical engineering mathematics (such as H.265+ bitrate formulas and HDD bay mapping) rather than arbitrary AI scoring algorithms."]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display font-medium text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-slate tracking-tight border-b border-brand-grey/20 pb-3","children":"3. Scoping Reviews & Response Commitments"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"We operate with consultative engineering discipline. Every project begins with independent advice on system architecture, site risk, and budget before any hardware specification is formally quoted."}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-brand-mist p-5 rounded-xl border border-brand-grey/20 space-y-2","children":[["$","span",null,{"className":"font-display font-medium text-xs text-brand-teal uppercase tracking-widest block flex items-center gap-2","children":[["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-circle-check w-4 h-4 text-brand-teal","children":[["$","circle","1mglay",{"cx":"12","cy":"12","r":"10"}],["$","path","dzmm74",{"d":"m9 12 2 2 4-4"}],"$undefined"]}]," Our Operational Commitment"]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"font-body font-normal text-xs md:text-sm text-brand-slate leading-relaxed","children":["We commit to responding to all formal scoping review requests within ",["$","strong",null,{"children":"one working day"}],". We do not advertise unverified emergency mobilization SLAs. Physical site surveys, technical audits, and formal design presentations are scheduled collaboratively with an engineering principal following your initial consultation."]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display font-medium text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-slate tracking-tight border-b border-brand-grey/20 pb-3","children":"4. System Design, Supply & Installation Standards"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Drievu Limited is not a box-shifter or a one-van installer. Where systems are subsequently quoted and commissioned, delivery is governed by the following engineering standards:"}],["$","ul",null,{"className":"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-brand-slate/80","children":[["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"font-medium text-brand-slate","children":"Quality-Verified Supply Chain:"}]," We specify quality-verified equipment from established manufacturers (such as IP PoE surveillance, addressable fire panels, and DIN-rail automation modules), engineered to withstand UK operating environments."]}],["$","li",null,{"children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"font-medium text-brand-slate","children":"British Standards Compliance:"}]," Systems are designed and specified to relevant British Standards, including BS EN guidelines (such as BS EN 50131 and BS EN 62676 for electronic security and surveillance)."]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-brand-mist p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-grey/20 space-y-4","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-2","children":[["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-file-text w-5 h-5 text-brand-teal","children":[["$","path","1rqfz7",{"d":"M15 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V7Z"}],["$","path","tnqrlb",{"d":"M14 2v4a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h4"}],["$","path","b1mrlr",{"d":"M10 9H8"}],["$","path","t4e002",{"d":"M16 13H8"}],["$","path","z1uh3a",{"d":"M16 17H8"}],"$undefined"]}],["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-display font-medium text-lg text-brand-slate tracking-tight","children":"5. Documented Handover Guarantee"}]]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/85","children":["We close the delivery gap inherent in the property management sector. We operate under the strict organizational standard: ",["$","em",null,{"children":"\"If it isn’t documented, it isn’t done\""}],"."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-xs md:text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-slate/85","children":"Every completed Drievu installation project closes with a structured, verifiable handover pack containing: as-installed device schedules, network and IP topology documentation, administrative credential records, end-user training verification, and data-processing guidance to support your ongoing UK GDPR compliance."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display font-medium text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-slate tracking-tight border-b border-brand-grey/20 pb-3","children":"6. Annual Maintenance Contracts (AMC)"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Systems are only as reliable as their ongoing maintenance. Long-term operational support, scheduled preventive maintenance visits, emergency call-out SLAs, and firmware management are provided exclusively under formal Annual Maintenance Contracts (AMC) across our Essential, Professional, and Commercial tiers. The specific response commitments governing active installations are defined within each client's individual AMC agreement."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"font-display font-medium text-xl md:text-2xl text-brand-slate tracking-tight border-b border-brand-grey/20 pb-3","children":"7. Intellectual Property & Website Content"}],["$","p",null,{"children":["All content, system schematics, deterministic calculation formulas, visual assets, and text published on ",["$","span",null,{"className":"font-mono text-xs","children":"drievu.com"}]," remain the intellectual property of Drievu Limited. You may download or print indicative system summaries for internal project evaluation, procurement due diligence, or tender structuring. Unauthorized commercial reproduction or automated scraping of our engineering calculation models is strictly prohibited."]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"space-y-4","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"fon